      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me with some info for a history lesson i'm putting together for my middle schoolers? i need to explain why there was such a huge wave of Italian immigrants coming into the US in the early 1900s and basically what the impact was like on the cities they moved into. thanks!",
